<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>{{Zend_Paginator_Adapter_DbSelect}} creates invalid SQL query for rows counting in a case if given query have {{GROUP BY}} clause with use of column alias instead of column itself. For example attempt to count rows for the following query:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>select a as some_column, b as other_column
from some_table 
where some_column='value'
group by some_column</code></pre>

<p>will produce SQL query:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>select count(distinct some_column)
from some_table 
where some_column='value'</code></pre>

<p>which will fail because there is no {{some_column}} column in table.</p>

    </div>
